---
description: SEO conventions for Next.js App Router in wokki-client
globs: app/**/*.tsx, lib/seo/**/*
---

- Use `getSiteUrl()` from `@/lib/seo/site` for static origin; set `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL` in production (no trailing slash).
- Public routes export `metadata` or `generateMetadata` via `buildPageMetadata({ title, description, path })`.
- Keep meaningful static HTML (at least one clear `h1` where appropriate).
- Heavy `generateMetadata` must use cached fetch with `revalidate` (see `lib/seo/fetch-public-seo.ts`).
- Extend `app/sitemap.ts` when adding indexable URL groups.
- Use `getSiteUrlFromRequest()` for JSON-LD when origin must match request host.
